Subject: [PATCH] HOOK: add necessary vendor hooks [1/1]

PD#SWPL-185970

Problem:
miss necessary vendor hooks

Solution:
add necessary vendor hooks

Verify:
on SC2

Change-Id: I81e59f4b493592929313b9202ca1ad5b3ac70a7f
Signed-off-by: Lei Zhang <lei.zhang@amlogic.com>
---
